this evening, i am really very happy,'' said douglas, speaking in german. ``i have made three films in germany, and so have had the opportunity to learn a little german.''
douglas' wife, anne, also attended the ceremony
the berlin film festival is europe's second-biggest annual movie event after the more prestigious festival in cannes, france
