the plane is in several pieces,'' ms. damiano said. ``there was a small bit of fire that was contained. there was no indication to the tower that the plane was in any danger prior to takeoff.''
she said witnesses reported hearing an explosion and seeing a fireball before the crash
it sounded like a blast or something,'' said mary h. ward, who lives in a mobile home about three miles from the airport. ``it was kind of muffled.''
