_israeli soldiers tangled with palestinian protesters in nablus and in the gaza strip, but no casualties were reported
_military sources denied charges by neil kinnock, head of britain's labor party, that israeli troops were using dumdum bullets against arab protesters. dumdum bullets expand explosively when they hit a target, causing greater damage
